## ðŸ”§ 1. Technical SEO

- [ ] HTTPS enabled (SSL active)
- [ ] Single canonical version (https + www OR non-www)
- [ ] HTTP â†’ HTTPS redirect enabled
- [ ] Mobile-friendly design
- [ ] Core Web Vitals optimized:
  - [ ] LCP < 2.5s
  - [ ] CLS < 0.1
  - [ ] INP < 200ms
- [ ] No crawl errors (Google Search Console)
- [ ] XML Sitemap available (`/sitemap.xml`)
- [ ] Robots.txt properly configured
- [ ] Noindex applied to dev / staging pages
- [ ] Optimized 404 error page
- [ ] No redirect chains or loops

